- AWS tool for DNS Services
- Support DNS Failover(can detect a website outage and can redirect people to website where it is working)
- Global traffic Management(create traffic policy that optimize your user experience)

- Fail over policy
- Also support weighted round robin, latency based routing, location based routing
- Main Route table can be modified but can not be deleted
- Each Subnet must be associated with route table
- Main route table is catch all for unassigned subnet
